    public class Vector
extends javafx.scene.shape.Line
    This class provides vectors, which are a core game component.

        Sets a vector between two given tiles.
        Parameters:
        oldTile - tile that represents the starting point of the vector.
        newTile - tile that represents the ending point of the vector.

      • bindNext

        public void bindNext​(RenderedTile currentTile,
                     javafx.scene.transform.Translate translation)
        Sets a vector between a tile and an other by using the route taken to said tile. The used route will be added to the current tile. The arrival point of the vector is the sum.
        Parameters:
        currentTile - tile that represents the starting point of the vector.
        translation - route taken to get to the current tile.
